def draw_sphere(X, Y, Z, color, edge_color):
    fig = plt.figure()
    ax = fig.add_subplot(111, projection='3d')
    
    ax.plot_surface(X, Y, Z, color=color, edgecolor=edge_color)

    ax.set_xlabel('X')
    ax.set_ylabel('Y')
    ax.set_zlabel('Z')

    plt.show()

def draw_pyramid(vertices, color, edge_color):
    fig = plt.figure()
    ax = fig.add_subplot(111, projection='3d')

    ax.plot_trisurf(vertices[[0, 1, 2], 0], vertices[[0, 1, 2], 1], vertices[[0, 1, 2], 2], color=color, alpha=0.6, edgecolor=edge_color)
    ax.plot_trisurf(vertices[[0, 2, 3], 0], vertices[[0, 2, 3], 1], vertices[[0, 2, 3], 2], color=color, alpha=0.6, edgecolor=edge_color)
    ax.plot_trisurf(vertices[[0, 1, 4], 0], vertices[[0, 1, 4], 1], vertices[[0, 1, 4], 2], color=color, alpha=0.6, edgecolor=edge_color)
    ax.plot_trisurf(vertices[[1, 2, 4], 0], vertices[[1, 2, 4], 1], vertices[[1, 2, 4], 2], color=color, alpha=0.6, edgecolor=edge_color)
    ax.plot_trisurf(vertices[[2, 3, 4], 0], vertices[[2, 3, 4], 1], vertices[[2, 3, 4], 2], color=color, alpha=0.6, edgecolor=edge_color)
    ax.plot_trisurf(vertices[[3, 0, 4], 0], vertices[[3, 0, 4], 1], vertices[[3, 0, 4], 2], color=color, alpha=0.6, edgecolor=edge_color)

    plt.show()

rotation_matix_x = np.array([
    [1, 0, 0],
    [0, np.cos(rotate_theta), -np.sin(rotate_theta)],
    [0, np.sin(rotate_theta), np.cos(rotate_theta)]
])

rotation_matix_y = np.array([
    [np.cos(rotate_theta), 0, np.sin(rotate_theta)],
    [0, 1, 0],
    [-np.sin(rotate_theta), 0, np.cos(rotate_theta)]
])

rotation_matix_z = np.array([
    [np.cos(rotate_theta), -np.sin(rotate_theta), 0],
    [np.sin(rotate_theta), np.cos(rotate_theta), 0],
    [0, 0, 1]
])

In [ ]:
def assign_face(vertices):
    return [
    [vertices[0], vertices[1], vertices[4]],  
    [vertices[1], vertices[2], vertices[4]], 
    [vertices[2], vertices[3], vertices[4]], 
    [vertices[3], vertices[0], vertices[4]],  
    [vertices[0], vertices[1], vertices[2], vertices[3]]  
    ]

def translate_pyramid_face(vertices):
    return [
    [vertices[0], vertices[1], vertices[4]],  # Front face
    [vertices[1], vertices[2], vertices[4]],  # Right face
    [vertices[2], vertices[3], vertices[4]],  # Back face
    [vertices[3], vertices[0], vertices[4]],  # Left face
    [vertices[0], vertices[1], vertices[2], vertices[3]]  #Base
    ]
In [311]:

In [312]:
def plot_translated_shapes(original, translated, color):
    fig = plt.figure(figsize=(10, 20))

    ax1 = fig.add_subplot(1, 2, 1, projection='3d')
    ax1.add_collection3d(Poly3DCollection(original, facecolors=color, linewidths=1, edgecolors='red', alpha=.5))
    ax1.set_title('Original Shape')
    ax1.set_xlabel('X')
    ax1.set_ylabel('Y')
    ax1.set_zlabel('Z')
    ax1.set_xlim([-40, 60])
    ax1.set_ylim([-40, 60])
    ax1.set_zlim([0, 50])

    ax2 = fig.add_subplot(1, 2, 2, projection='3d')
    ax2.add_collection3d(Poly3DCollection(translated, facecolors=color, linewidths=1, edgecolors='red', alpha=.5))
    ax2.set_title('Translated Shape')
    ax2.set_xlabel('X')
    ax2.set_ylabel('Y')
    ax2.set_zlabel('Z')
    ax2.set_xlim([-40, 60])
    ax2.set_ylim([-40, 60])
    ax2.set_zlim([0, 50])

    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.show()

def plot_rotated_spheres(x1, y1, z1, x2, y2, z2, color, edgecolor):
    fig = plt.figure(figsize=(10, 30))

    ax1 = fig.add_subplot(1, 2, 1, projection='3d')
    ax1.plot_surface(x1, y1, z1, color=color, edgecolor=edgecolor)
    ax1.set_title('Original Sphere')
    ax1.set_xlabel('X')
    ax1.set_ylabel('Y')
    ax1.set_zlabel('Z')
    ax1.set_xlim([-100, 100])
    ax1.set_ylim([-100, 100])
    ax1.set_zlim([-100, 100])

    ax2 = fig.add_subplot(1, 2, 2, projection='3d')
    ax2.plot_surface(x2, y1, z1, color=color, edgecolor=edgecolor)
    ax2.set_title('Rotated Sphere with respect to X')
    ax2.set_xlabel('X')
    ax2.set_ylabel('Y')
    ax2.set_zlabel('Z')
    ax2.set_xlim([-100, 100])
    ax2.set_ylim([-100, 100])
    ax2.set_zlim([-100, 100])

    ax3 = fig.add_subplot(2, 2, 1, projection='3d')
    ax3.plot_surface(x1, y2, z1, color=color, edgecolor=edgecolor)
    ax3.set_title('Rotated Sphere with respect to Y')
    ax3.set_xlabel('X')
    ax3.set_ylabel('Y')
    ax3.set_zlabel('Z')
    ax3.set_xlim([-100, 100])
    ax3.set_ylim([-100, 100])
    ax3.set_zlim([-100, 100])

    ax4 = fig.add_subplot(2, 2, 2, projection='3d')
    ax4.plot_surface(x1, y1, z2, color=color, edgecolor=edgecolor)
    ax4.set_title('Rotated Sphere with respect to Z')
    ax4.set_xlabel('X')
    ax4.set_ylabel('Y')
    ax4.set_zlabel('Z')
    ax4.set_xlim([-100, 100])
    ax4.set_ylim([-100, 100])
    ax4.set_zlim([-100, 100])

    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.show()
